//* Program name: The Tax Machine                                       *
//*                                                                     *
//* Written by: Greylen Fernandez                                       *
//*                                                                     *
//* Purpose: Calculate the final price of marked up items               *
//*                                                                     *
//* Inputs: User input                                                  *
//*                                                                     *
//* Outputs: The calculated prices                                      *
//*                                                                     *
//* Calls: Nothing                                                      *
//*                                                                     *
//* Structure: BEGIN                                                    *
//*                        Straight line code no sub-processes          *
//*                   STOP                                              *
//*                        End of Program                               *
